issau_card_full.jpg", "news_site": "ESA", "summary": "From the ESA Blogs.", "published_at": "2026-07-17T08:00:00Z", "updated_at": "2026-07-17T08:30:14.879462Z", "featured": false, "launches": [], "events": []}, {"id": 39039, "title": "A Tide-Fueled Trove of Biodiversity in Guinea-Bissau", "authors": [{"name": "NASA", "socials": null}], "url": "https://science.nasa.gov/earth/earth-observatory/a-tide-fueled-trove-of-biodiversity-in-guinea-bissau/", "image_url": "https://assets.science.nasa.gov/dynamicimage/assets/science/esd/eo/images/iotd/2026/a-tide-fueled-trove-of-biodiversity-in-guinea-bissau/bijagosarchipelago_oli_20251128.jpg", "news_site": "NASA", "summary": "The expansive mudflats, sandy beaches, and mangrove forests of the Bijag\u00f3s archipelago support an array of migratory shorebirds and large numbers of sea turtles.", "published_at": "2026-07-17T04:01:00Z", "updated_at": "2026-07-17T04:10:09.261945Z", "featured": false, "launches": [], "events": []}, {"id": 39038, "title": "No-Go For Starship Today, Next Try Maybe Next Week", "authors": [{"name": "Marcia Smith", "socials": null}], "url": "https://spacepolicyonline.com/news/no-go-for-starship-today-next-try-maybe-next-week/", "image_url": "https://spacepolicyonline.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Starship-no-go-July-16-2026-300x170.jpg", "news_site": "SpacePolicyOnline.com", "summary": "SpaceX\u2019s first attempt to launch Starship on its 13th test flight today didn\u2019t go as planned. At the moment of startup, some of the 33 engines on Starship\u2019s first stage [\u2026]", "published_at": "2026-07-17T01:46:19Z", "updated_at": "2026-07-17T01:50:15.333988Z", "featured": false, "launches": [], "events": []}, {"id": 39037, "title": "SpaceX aborts Starship Flight 13 launch attempt", "authors": [{"name": "Jeff Foust", "socials": {"x": "https://x.com/jeff_foust", "youtube": "", "instagram": "", "linkedin": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/jefffoust", "mastodon": "https://mastodon.social/@jfoust", "bluesky": "htt